{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100390/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1734117201\" /><br><br>Zellige : The Tilemaker of Granada is a meditative and relaxing historical game, set in medieval Al-Andalus, where you play as a skilled tilemaker and design intricate Islamic mosaic patterns to decorate a merchant family's palace.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100390/extras/atelier_de_dessin_square_600x600.png?t=1734117201\" /><br><br>You will be able to create a various array of mosaics in all styles, following traditional techniques or let your creativity flow !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100390/extras/market.jpg?t=1734117201\" /><br><br>We really aim to bring you a calm experience, the sort of game you can play to unwind after a long day at work, and to get that sense of satisfaction that comes with creating something of your own. The palace is a fully explorable 3D environment, which you can walk around and admire in first-person. While doing so, you'll be able to talk to its inhabitants, the Dhahbans. They are a wealthy, well-travelled merchant family, and their home is filled with souvenirs and artefacts from across the Islamic world which will help you find inspiration and learn new techniques!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Art of Maghreb","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2100390/e606ad6e4b09bf5c2f57cccfc8e15e2be8ecddc6.jpg"},{"name":"Art of Mashriq","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2100390/e177ac1f2d7f1e390cb26a63ba4466693f33dca8.jpg"},{"name":"Art of Hind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2100390/5d0f8d99abc7206b80a0c8d69c4542cae784d71e.jpg"},{"name":"Art of Faris","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.co